  _NPCName: Sunny
  _lines:
  - Is that- A ring!
  - Oh-
  - Oh my goodness!!
  - Awwww it's so cute-
  - I love it!
  - It, Looks like the sun one you made me a while ago!
  - I tried my best making it that time
  - I saw this one a few moons ago, and it reminded me of you
  - The swirls, and the stones imbedded match us
  - I hope this brings you as much joy as you bring me
  - I love you
